    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Assessment package accepted for submission to regulatory review. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated and documented; 7 factors assessed with achieved levels recorded, 6 factors flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed for pressure head and wall shear stress validation results. Note: hemolysis index validation result (VR-03) characterizes biological assay variability qualitatively only; inherent run-to-run scatter in NIH measurements acknowledged in narrative without a structured UQ node, consistent with current laboratory capability. The package accurately represents the credibility state of the model and supports the regulatory submission decision.",
